{"tid":2462072,"cid":21,"subCid":5,"title":"You're Beautiful","createTime":"2021-03-25T18:28:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T18:49:29.000Z","uid":153781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"07426214690db78fb18e62dfbbd4f9106f82a44f","tid":2462072,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T18:28:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oofSnsGkops\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoofSnsGkops&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GsF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=26286f77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oofSnsGkops</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMy life is brilliant<br />\nMy life is brilliant<br />\nMy love is pure<br />\nI saw an angel<br />\nOf that I'm sure<br />\nShe smiled at me on the subway<br />\nShe was with another man<br />\nBut I won't lose no sleep on that<br />\n'Cause I've got a plan<br />\n<br />\nYou're beautiful<br />\nYou're beautiful<br />\nYou're beautiful, it's true<br />\nI saw your face in a crowded place<br />\nAnd I don't know what to do<br />\n'Cause I'll never be with you"},{"pid":"a97bf9116ca56419d821ce40c6a09fda94e891a7","tid":2462072,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T18:30:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uWeqeQkjLto\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuWeqeQkjLto&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GsF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=6c25bf34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uWeqeQkjLto</a><br />\n<br />\nI would call you every Saturday night<br />\nAnd we'd both stay out 'til the morning light<br />\nAnd we sang, &quot;Here we go again&quot;"},{"pid":"b83099ab757842f07df3751d6ffef4fce4bb0c8e","tid":2462072,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T18:35:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wVyggTKDcOE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwVyggTKDcOE&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GsF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=5025e1d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wVyggTKDcOE</a><br />\n<br />\nGoodbye my lover<br />\nGoodbye my friend<br />\nYou have been the one<br />\nYou have been the one for me"},{"pid":"942d7cf02c038d3406e50012871a1773ec91646e","tid":2462072,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T18:42:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/b3c32wBYdU0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fb3c32wBYdU0&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GsF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=95360b72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/b3c32wBYdU0</a><br />\n<br />\nI'm not calling for a second chance<br />\nI'm screaming at the top of my voice<br />\nGive me reason, but don't give me choice<br />\n'Cause I'll just make the same mistake"},{"pid":"8cb2a9f57f88f3c16cfd18716cfbe14167e3c3ab","tid":2462072,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T18:44:40.000Z","msg":"十歲那年愛上了James blunt的聲音"},{"pid":"76843b871bc574f08b8ee2ca534fe9c9421b21bf","tid":2462072,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T18:44:50.000Z","msg":"巴打個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e7c9f0ca7cdaea1341346941a5a206187029cf","tid":2462072,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76843b871bc574f08b8ee2ca534fe9c9421b21bf","tid":2462072,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T18:44:50.000Z","msg":"巴打個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T18:45:06.000Z","msg":"憂鬱小生"},{"pid":"24a4448a6614b8e36c0e4d57ee31c951aca422e2","tid":2462072,"uid":198023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T18:47:35.000Z","msg":"個妹仔見到個老爺呢 就話喇: you are so handsome, you are so smart"},{"pid":"870f4fb3264be07b1b92e70744ab7c0e27d35190","tid":2462072,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24a